Golden Boy is an upcoming American crime drama series created by Nicholas Wootton, which is being produced by Berlanti Television and Warner Bros. Television. CBS placed a series order in May 2012. The series will debut on CBS on Tuesday, February 26, 2013, at 10:00 pm ET. Another episode will air the following Tuesday, and then the series moves to Fridays starting March 8, 2013.
Premise.
The series follows the successful, meteoric rise—from age 26 to 34—of an ambitious cop who becomes the youngest police commissioner in New York City history.
